{"tid":1363226,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[未來] 有咗機械人，以後個極權仲需要鎮暴警察同白衫人？","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T06:14:17.000Z","uid":260806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b62cb03047ad342ffe6fae20bed353ddcd297883","tid":1363226,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rW9WmA5okpE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrW9WmA5okpE&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUYD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=639de526\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rW9WmA5okpE</a><br />\n<br />\n轉眼之間，機械人已經發展到呢種水平。如果將來中共大規模製造廉價機械人，充當鎮暴警察，香港人嘅未來會相當危險。人類鎮暴警察同白衫黑社會都會失業，巡邏、執勤、制服犯人都會係機械人嘅工作。你再鬧佢「黑警」、「毅進仔」都冇用。佢哋連長盾都唔需要，你永遠打唔到佢。<br />\n<br />\n15 至 20 年之內，呢種嘢一定會出現。如果香港唔趁呢個世代來之前，建立一個好制度來保障人權。後果真係不堪設想。"},{"pid":"31c9ff38b235fac66f43f65de9b4819b59bbf906","tid":1363226,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:13:16.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"046285d6e2bb3337167add7ffe8c59b822660293","tid":1363226,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"心水清"},{"pid":"2ae10f94ba536a259d0dc14fd1465143c175698d","tid":1363226,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"已經唔人對人，而係全部人面對人類嘅惡意"}]}